The 7 foods groups used for tabulation of this indicator were: (a) grains, roots and tubers; (b) legumes and nuts; (c) dairy products (milk, yogurt, cheese); (d) flesh foods (meat, fish, poultry and liver/organ meats); (e) eggs; (f) vitamin-A rich fruits and vegetables; (g) other fruits and vegetables.
